# Per-service log folders (src/.../<Service>/Logs). The bare `Logs` pattern is
# root-anchored and only matched the repo-root /Logs, so ~388 MB of runtime logs
# were leaking into the backend build context and images (size + PHI exposure).
# `**/Logs` matches Logs at any depth, including the repo root.
**/Logs

